1
00:00:58,053 --> 00:01:01,029
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,029 --> 00:01:02,999
=Episode 5=

3
00:01:02,999 --> 00:01:07,021
(You're Such a Great Actor)

4
00:01:07,021 --> 00:01:11,424
(Fufeng Pavilion)

5
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:16,319
Now let me teach you
how to speak like Zhaoxi.

6
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,920
Keep your voice light, not too deep.

7
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:38,680
Part your lips slowly.

8
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:04,799
Why don't you

9
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:09,240
start by calling me "dear"?

10
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:13,719
Dear.

11
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,639
Wrong.

12
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,919
Dear.

13
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,680
That's right.

14
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:50,159
Keep practicing.

15
00:02:59,008 --> 00:03:02,464
(Virtue of Heaven and Earth)

16
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,319
(Yuluo.)

17
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:09,560
(If I had competed to be the family head
instead of pursuing martial arts,)

18
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:13,680
(would things
have been different between us?)

19
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:27,143
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

20
00:03:28,927 --> 00:03:34,508
♪Old dreams flow like melodious poetry♪

21
00:03:35,597 --> 00:03:38,872
♪Memories fade like the passing years♪

22
00:03:38,872 --> 00:03:41,504
♪The past events leave us confused♪

23
00:03:41,504 --> 00:03:47,824
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

24
00:03:49,056 --> 00:03:56,192
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

25
00:03:56,192 --> 00:04:00,576
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

26
00:04:00,576 --> 00:04:02,816
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

27
00:04:02,816 --> 00:04:09,834
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

28
00:04:09,834 --> 00:04:16,384
♪With nothing but memories left♪

29
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:25,439
(Now, I have to watch you
marry someone else.)

30
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:28,199
(You only met him a few days ago.)

31
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,279
(Are you truly fond of him?)

32
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:36,000
I didn't sleep well last night.

33
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:38,639
Those assassins chased me
all the way to the Gu Mansion.

34
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:44,800
Luckily, the guards discovered them
and saved me in time.

35
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,199
You must have been startled.

36
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:51,120
It's alright, but I've been thinking.

37
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,120
I'm afraid someone did this on purpose.

38
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:56,639
They think I paid off those assassins
to stage this act.

39
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,920
What makes you say that?

40
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,959
I intended to bring those assassins

41
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,800
and talk to you about what to do.

42
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,959
But Chaosheng stopped me
before I even left.

43
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:15,399
I'm not sure if I should say this.

44
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,439
What do you think
about Zhaoxi being attacked?

45
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,920
Do you really believe
that Zhaoxi ran into bandits?

46
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,600
Xuanji.

47
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:44,319
It's only you and me here.

48
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:47,000
Feel free to speak your mind.

49
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:52,120
Zhaoxi rarely goes out.
Why did he leave the city that day?

50
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:55,120
I found it suspicious and dug into it.

51
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:58,720
It turns out
that Chaosheng didn't return those days.

52
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:02,360
He met Zhaoxi after Father arranged
for your wedding.

53
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:07,319
You don't look surprised.
So you know this all along.

54
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:12,240
Right, you're about to
lead the Xuanji Pavilion.

55
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:15,319
Such a small matter
wouldn't escape your notice.

56
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:21,160
However, there's one thing
you certainly don't know.

57
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:26,519
Chaosheng once sent
a famous assassin to kill Zhaoxi.

58
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:30,959
Watch your words.

59
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:34,319
I heard you visited
the assassin Leng Yan.

60
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:37,560
But by the time you arrived,
he was already dead.

61
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:21,360
But the person who silenced him
didn't know he had a mistress.

62
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:23,399
She wasn't home and escaped the ordeal.

63
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:28,079
I felt sorry for her
and kept her at Nichang Workshop.

64
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,240
If you want to meet her,

65
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:35,519
I can bring her over
to take your measures these days.

66
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:40,480
Since you have doubts,
why don't you inform the family head

67
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,720
or the authorities?

68
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:44,040
The authorities concluded

69
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,839
that Zhaoxi was attacked by the bandits.

70
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:49,199
Father can't be worried
about these matters at this moment.

71
00:07:50,399 --> 00:07:52,439
I was restless
after the attack yesterday.

72
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:55,040
If that person
is trying to be the family head,

73
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:58,639
then Zhaoxi and I
won't be the last victims.

74
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:03,439
Chaosheng wants to be the family head.

75
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:05,040
And what about you?

76
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:10,360
Chaosheng has
managed the shops for years.

77
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:13,919
He's quite recognized,
but outsiders are clueless.

78
00:08:13,919 --> 00:08:17,879
Everyone in the family knows
that the Xuanji Pavilion is the core.

79
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:22,920
Whoever wants to be the new family head
needs your support.

80
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:30,480
I know you suspect
that I sent assassins for Zhaoxi.

81
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:32,120
But if it were me,

82
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:35,279
I would never
attempt something so clumsy.

83
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:40,039
There are ways to kill someone
without getting noticed, right?

84
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:44,679
For example,

85
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:46,440
with poison.

86
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:51,240
What makes you say that?

87
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:54,080
You're an expert
in the art of poisoning.

88
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:57,080
The poisons and antidotes
you develop are priceless.

89
00:08:58,159 --> 00:09:01,039
Leng Yan died from a strange poison
with a smile on his face

90
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:03,240
and blood oozing out
from seven orifices.

91
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:06,080
That reminds me
of your Laughing Netherworld.

92
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:10,840
It seems the culprit is determined
to throw this mud at me.

93
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:16,919
Master Chaosheng barged in Fufeng Pavilion.
He's with Master Zhaoxi now.

94
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:23,080
What brings you here today, Chaosheng?

95
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:28,600
I haven't been well
after that heavy snow.

96
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:32,960
So I invited Physician Li over.
He can also check on you.

97
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,240
I hope you recover soon.

98
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:37,919
That would put my mind at ease.

99
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:44,159
Well, thank you, Chaosheng.

100
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:53,840
(Light steps, calluses in the palm.)

101
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,440
(He is no ordinary physician.)

102
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,720
(He's more like a martial artist.)

103
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:28,320
Well?

104
00:10:38,399 --> 00:10:40,000
Just as you predicted.

105
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:43,879
Both his old ailments and new injuries
need careful recuperation.

106
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:47,480
You may leave.

107
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:48,759
Understood.

108
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:54,919
The court has ordered to eradicate
the bandits outside the city.

109
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:59,279
Do you remember anything
about the bandits who attacked you?

110
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,024
It was chaotic.

111
00:11:02,176 --> 00:11:03,679
I can't remember much.

112
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,679
Why aren't you wearing that jade pendant

113
00:11:11,679 --> 00:11:12,879
you have had since childhood?

114
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:19,879
I suppose it was lost
while I was under attack.

115
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:27,879
Master Chaosheng, Prince Rui brought
a masterpiece to enjoy with you.

116
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,440
He's heading straight here.

117
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,120
Should we...?

118
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,639
You are in high spirits.

119
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:42,159
I'm surprised
to see you here, Chaosheng.

120
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:48,600
But the family head
just sent a physician over.

121
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:51,799
And you brought another physician.

122
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:56,799
If others learn about it,
I fear it may spark gossip

123
00:11:57,279 --> 00:12:00,360
that you distrust the physician
sent by the family head.

124
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:04,519
Since you won't accept my goodwill,

125
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,600
let's say I've overstepped.

126
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:11,120
We can't keep Prince Rui waiting.
Bring him in.

127
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,240
Understood.

128
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,279
Dear.

129
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:22,759
Chaosheng,
Zhaoxi hasn't fully recovered.

130
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:26,528
Please excuse us from joining you.
We won't see you out.

131
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:08,440
Your acting has truly
reached new heights.

132
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:10,120
I'm deeply impressed.

133
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:15,679
I'm still having a cold.

134
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,039
You're burning.

135
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,519
Rest well.

136
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:56,080
Master, Gu Zhaoxi
is indeed chronically ill.

137
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:58,840
Nothing unusual.

138
00:14:06,496 --> 00:14:13,952
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

139
00:14:18,279 --> 00:14:20,200
Master, the east wind has arrived.

140
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:27,240
If anyone comes, tell them I'm unwell

141
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,159
and can't see them.

142
00:14:28,919 --> 00:14:31,399
Master, are you truly going?

143
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,799
Of course.

144
00:14:37,879 --> 00:14:38,679
But

145
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:41,480
I'm not sure if my "husband"...

146
00:14:42,559 --> 00:14:45,120
I've sent people
to investigate his former residence.

147
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:48,279
His connections are simple,
and the facts check out.

148
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:51,919
Master, do you still have concerns?

149
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,159
He's way too simple,

150
00:14:55,279 --> 00:14:57,039
which raises concerns.

151
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:01,279
We can't keep Prince Rui waiting.
Bring him in.

152
00:15:01,399 --> 00:15:02,200
Understood.

153
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:10,519
Find out if he knows Prince Rui.

154
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,240
Understood.

155
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,159
Xuan Qing.

156
00:15:17,919 --> 00:15:20,720
Make a cold-dispelling medicine for him.

157
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,279
Understood.

158
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:48,799
Both Qing Que and Xuan Wu
are finally away on missions.

159
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:52,039
Everyone went drinking except for us.

160
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,120
And we need to patrol.

161
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:57,120
Enough, everyone's gone.
Let's hope nothing goes wrong.

162
00:18:08,359 --> 00:18:09,599
Check the Xuanji Pavilion.

163
00:18:37,039 --> 00:18:39,400
The Earth Unit did a great job
in the challenge.

164
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:43,119
This junior reminds me of
the former Pavilion Master's demeanor.

165
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:49,319
It appears this Heaven mission

166
00:18:50,119 --> 00:18:51,880
still requires your handling.

167
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,839
It's not time yet.

168
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:01,119
Xuanji Pavilion

169
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:04,240
collects tips rather than
carrying out assassinations.

170
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,759
To bring back the tips,

171
00:19:07,079 --> 00:19:11,319
staying resolved
often outweighs defeating enemies.

172
00:19:26,784 --> 00:19:28,256
(Earth)

173
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:32,680
Gu Yuluo of Earth Unit
requests to take on the Heaven mission.

174
00:19:40,759 --> 00:19:41,799
Hurry up. Search.

175
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,039
Master.

176
00:19:51,119 --> 00:19:53,160
Search over there.
Don't let them escape.

177
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:55,319
Find him first. I'll handle them.

178
00:20:07,839 --> 00:20:08,640
Dear.

179
00:20:44,581 --> 00:20:49,644
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

180
00:20:50,181 --> 00:20:55,502
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

181
00:20:56,069 --> 00:21:02,697
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

182
00:21:02,697 --> 00:21:07,461
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

183
00:21:07,461 --> 00:21:09,797
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

184
00:21:09,797 --> 00:21:16,497
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

185
00:21:16,497 --> 00:21:23,269
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

186
00:21:23,269 --> 00:21:30,405
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

187
00:21:30,405 --> 00:21:34,789
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

188
00:21:34,789 --> 00:21:37,413
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

189
00:21:37,413 --> 00:21:44,047
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

190
00:21:44,047 --> 00:21:50,597
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

191
00:21:50,597 --> 00:21:57,721
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

192
